  • Accelerate Digital Transformation with Google at the Core

    The marketing landscape is changing quickly and the need to bring data and clarity into the decision-making process at scale is critical.

    Merkle | Cardinal Path is the worlds leading partner for Google Marketing Platform services and solutions. Our global team of experts partner with enterprises to tackle their most complex digital marketing problems and surface the greatest opportunities.

    From a data-informed roadmap to streamlined martech, and meaningful digital activation - we help brands build market share by delivering high-quality, data-first solutions with Google at the core.

Delivering a Modern Martech Stack: Google Marketing Platform

Google Marketing Platform (GMP) helps brands meet the new and emerging challenges head-on.

As a leading GMP partner and the worlds largest Google Analytics 360 Sales Partner, we help our clients deploy the Google Marketing Platform as a fully integrated suite for robust upstream capabilities.

Coupled with our proprietary solutions we empower brands and agencies to provide an optimized, future-proof, and privacy-hardened digital experience.
